H.P. 1268 House of Representatives, May 5, 2025
An Act Regarding Sun-grown Cultivation in the Medical Use and
Adult Use Cannabis Industries
Received by the Clerk of the House on May 1, 2025. Referred to the Committee on
Veterans and Legal Affairs pursuant to Joint Rule 308.2 and ordered printed pursuant to Joint
Rule 401.
ROBERT B. HUNT
Clerk
Presented by Representative OSHER of Orono.
Cosponsored by Senator HICKMAN of Kennebec and
Representatives: BOYER of Poland, CHAPMAN of Auburn, DILL of Old Town, PLUECKER
